        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p>NMJ Lovers | Annika and Josh</p>",
        "description": "<p>For this chapter of NMJ Lovers, we step into Jordy and Tom’s story. One shaped by growing up together, embracing change side by side, and finding comfort in the life they’ve built along the way.</p><p>They first met at a party in their late teens, encouraged there by a mutual friend with a clear intention in mind. Between late-night conversation and a shared box of KFC, something effortless began. </p><p>What followed was years of growing together through new cities, shifting seasons of life, evolving careers, and changing friendships. <em>Through it all, their relationship remained grounded in something steady.</em> A deep sense of loyalty, partnership, and choosing one another at every stage.</p><p>A love story rooted in growth, familiarity, and the beauty of building a life together.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
    "text_with_media_aj4gXB": {
